Rory McIlroy sent Andy Murray a text apologising for being unable to attend the Scot's US Open match against Robin Haase on Monday, and reciprocate the support he was given by the British No 1 at the golf in New Jersey last week.

It is not known if his former fiancee Caroline Wozniacki playing the same day was a factor. 

David Beckham  is expected to attend this week, possibly to support Murray.

